      "instruction": "<p>Whilst the chicken is browning, deseed the <strong>pepper<span class=\"text-danger\">[s] </span></strong>(scrape the seeds and pith out with a teaspoon) and cut into rough bite-sized pieces</p><p>Chop the <strong>tomatoes</strong> into wedges</p><p>Peel and quarter the <strong>shallots</strong></p><p>Crush the <strong>garlic clove<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> open by squashing them with the side of a knife and discard the skin<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></p>",
