    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>smoked paprika</strong>,<strong> ground cumin</strong> and <strong>ground coriander</strong> to the dish</p><p>Add the <strong>shallot quarters</strong>, <strong>crushed garlic</strong>, <strong>chopped pepper </strong>and <strong>tomato wedges</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and give everything a good mix up</p>",
